"broom clean,"</i>

43:23.747 --> 43:26.181
<i>but they couldn't
be bothered.</i>

43:26.216 --> 43:28.016
Where'd they go?

43:28.051 --> 43:30.019
<i>Not sure.</i>

43:30.053 --> 43:32.287
The wife was...

43:32.322 --> 43:35.857
was always talking about Paris.

43:43.099 --> 43:45.467
Look, mommy... ghosts.

44:03.818 --> 44:05.452
