47:09.670 --> 47:11.437
Go on now.

47:11.472 --> 47:14.340
- Washed in the blood of the lamb.
- Lord Jesus.

47:15.609 --> 47:17.042
Okay, fine.

47:17.076 --> 47:19.444
Amen.

47:19.478 --> 47:22.346
- Give unto the lord.
- Hallelujah.

47:38.327 --> 47:40.862
