47:58.377 --> 48:01.479
I will.

48:12.222 --> 48:16.458
Do you accept Jesus
as your savior?

48:16.492 --> 48:17.826
Yes yes.

48:17.860 --> 48:19.561
Am I supposed to hold...?

48:21.563 --> 48:23.497
